confoo - configuration file lookup library (currently part of migrit)

configen - promise based configuration file usage library

httpromise - promise based api resource usage library in node

migrit 
  - environment agnostic mysql schema migration tool and database snapshotter
  - invoked via command line
      e.g. 
        $ migrit [up|down|import|export] [options]

routest 
  - api testing framework
  - included in testing files, invoked by node
      e.g. 
        $ node testing-file.js

devup 
  - feature management layer 
  - most typically accessed through gulp, grunt, etc
